      <title>中国考虑分两步降低抵押贷款利率以保护银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/china-weighs-cutting-mortgage-rates-in-two-steps-to-shield-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国正考虑分两步降低高达 5.3 万亿美元的抵押贷款利率，以降低数百万家庭的借贷成本，同时缓解银行系统的利润紧缩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/china-weighs-cutting-mortgage-rates-in-two-steps-to-shield-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 08:30:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及总统塞西访问土耳其，试图修复与埃尔多安的不和</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/egypt-s-el-sisi-visits-turkey-in-move-to-repair-erdogan-discord</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及总统阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·塞西将于周三在安卡拉会见土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安，两国寻求修复近期紧张的关系，并在能源、国防和加沙战争方面开展更密切的合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/egypt-s-el-sisi-visits-turkey-in-move-to-repair-erdogan-discord</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 08:20:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>企业家对工党的资本利得税计划提出警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/entrepreneurs-raise-the-alarm-over-labour-s-capital-gains-tax-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者和企业家警告称，如果工党政府在十月份的预算中提高资本利得税，英国将失去快速增长的初创企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/entrepreneurs-raise-the-alarm-over-labour-s-capital-gains-tax-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰准备应对国际货币基金组织要求其货币贬值和降息的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ukraine-braces-for-imf-pressure-to-devalue-currency-cut-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，乌克兰官员预计国际货币基金组织本周将敦促乌克兰加快货币贬值、降低利率并加大增税力度，以填补该国的预算缺口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ukraine-braces-for-imf-pressure-to-devalue-currency-cut-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 07:37:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌干达的鲍比·瓦因与警方发生争执后情况稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/uganda-s-bobi-wine-in-stable-condition-after-police-altercation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体报道，乌干达反对派领导人罗伯特·基亚古拉尼（Robert Kyagulanyi，化名鲍比·瓦恩（Bobi Wine））在首都坎帕拉郊区与警方对峙时受伤，目前正在医院康复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/uganda-s-bobi-wine-in-stable-condition-after-police-altercation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 07:29:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国签署协议改造数十年历史的南非铁路</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/china-signs-deal-to-revamp-decades-old-southern-african-railway</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国周三签署了一项改造铁路的协议，这将帮助非洲第二大铜生产国、内陆国家赞比亚通过坦桑尼亚出口铜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/china-signs-deal-to-revamp-decades-old-southern-african-railway</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 06:12:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰称俄罗斯袭击利沃夫造成 5 人死亡，数十人受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ukraine-says-russian-strike-kills-5-injures-dozens-in-lviv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰市长安德烈·萨多维伊周三表示，俄罗斯对利沃夫发动了联合空袭，这是对这座西部城市的一次罕见袭击，造成包括一名小学生在内的 5 人死亡，至少 35 人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/ukraine-says-russian-strike-kills-5-injures-dozens-in-lviv</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 05:58:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国新总理皮查伊保留内阁成员，担任财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/new-thailand-pm-keeps-pichai-as-finance-chief-in-cabinet-line-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理巴东丹·西那瓦公布了新内阁阵容，保留皮猜担任财政部长，这一举动表明泰国在振兴东南亚第二大经济体的重任中将保持政策的连续性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/new-thailand-pm-keeps-pichai-as-finance-chief-in-cabinet-line-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 04:14:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基密谋改组，乌克兰内阁大选结果出炉，库列巴加入其中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/three-ukrainian-ministers-resign-in-broader-cabinet-shuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰外交部长德米特罗·库列巴于周三提交辞呈，在外界猜测乌克兰政府准备进行大规模改组之际，两天内内阁部长总数增至六名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/three-ukrainian-ministers-resign-in-broader-cabinet-shuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:54:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
